descriptionHtml:
Here is a saved game for the Lunari Race. You can find Jasmine at Riverwood. She is at level 1 with plenty of loot to get you started.

I used  Caliente and the CBBE body
Lunari Race mod - http://http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21602
Apachii Skyhair - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168

Thanks to all the modders for their hard work.
author: DrJoe
